  "remarks": "LLC Drake is a Russian trade company. It is also a subsidiary of both LLC Alabuga Machinery (50 %) and LLC Alabuga Development (50 %). LLC Alabuga Machinery is also a subsidiary (100 %) of the LLC Alabuga Development, which is a subsidiary (100 %) of the JSC “Alabuga” Special Economic Zone of Industrial and Production Type (listed by the Union since 18 December 2023), which is thus the indirect owner of LLC Drake.",
